caseTitle: Commissioner Inland Revenue Z-III v. M/s. MSC Switzerland Geneva & others
tagline: (1) Discussion on Section 107, 109 and 44 of Income Tax Ordinance 2001. (2) Avoidance of Double Taxation in view of Double Taxation Treaties. (3) Article 31 of the Vienna Convention 1969. (4) Review jurisdiction under Article 188 of the Constitution read with Order XXVI of Supreme Court Rules 1980 and Order XLVII, Rule 1 CPC.
